And here is how you can get back the term vectors from ES:

    TermVectorsResponse resp = client.prepareTermVectors().setIndex(&quot;indexName&quot;)
                              .setType(&quot;docType&quot;).setId(&quot;docId&quot;).execute().actionGet();
        
    XContentBuilder builder;
